640
00:28:01,550 --> 00:28:03,100
I'll help everyone make money.

641
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:05,020
In short,

642
00:28:05,660 --> 00:28:06,620
no matter what,

643
00:28:07,260 --> 00:28:08,420
Dian Lao'er cannot

644
00:28:08,500 --> 00:28:09,340
get any shares.

645
00:28:13,460 --> 00:28:14,300
Man,

646
00:28:15,820 --> 00:28:16,900
you'll have to work hard.

647
00:28:17,820 --> 00:28:18,660
I'm fine.

648
00:28:19,860 --> 00:28:21,020
I'll think about it.

649
00:28:28,430 --> 00:28:30,590
When you cheat in my territory,

650
00:28:31,260 --> 00:28:33,540
you should've known this would happen.

651
00:28:34,780 --> 00:28:35,780
Lao'er, please spare me.

652
00:28:35,780 --> 00:28:37,260
I beg you, I...

653
00:28:37,380 --> 00:28:38,220
Hello?

654
00:28:38,260 --> 00:28:39,100
Here, here.

655
00:28:39,380 --> 00:28:40,540
I've got an idea for you.

656
00:28:42,260 --> 00:28:43,500
Your mother

657
00:28:43,940 --> 00:28:46,060
has shares in Tuan Island, right?

658
00:28:48,220 --> 00:28:49,900
Let her use her shares

659
00:28:50,820 --> 00:28:51,860
to exchange for your hand.

660
00:28:52,100 --> 00:28:53,660
This deal's not a loss for you.

661
00:28:53,660 --> 00:28:55,860
Of course not.

662
00:28:59,580 --> 00:29:00,420
Come on.

