00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:11,660
But

687
00:31:11,780 --> 00:31:13,540
Bin's really invested in this.

688
00:31:13,860 --> 00:31:15,580
From what I know about him,

689
00:31:15,580 --> 00:31:17,380
he'll try to figure out a way
to solve it.

690
00:31:19,420 --> 00:31:20,260
Let him be.

691
00:31:23,220 --> 00:31:24,180
Never mind.

692
00:31:25,540 --> 00:31:26,660
I can't control him anyway.

