00:31:29,260 --> 00:31:30,100
Come on.

694
00:31:30,740 --> 00:31:32,180
Aren't we trying to catch someone?

695
00:31:32,300 --> 00:31:34,100
Why are we strolling
around the food street?

696
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:36,260
They are not

697
00:31:37,260 --> 00:31:38,300
mutually exclusive, right?

698
00:31:39,060 --> 00:31:39,900
What do you mean?

699
00:31:40,610 --> 00:31:41,260
Let me ask you.

700
00:31:41,260 --> 00:31:42,580
If you had to choose right now,

701
00:31:42,580 --> 00:31:43,920
