00:31:49,860 --> 00:31:51,260
You came from Binjiang to Ninghai.

706
00:31:51,260 --> 00:31:52,620
You want claypot rice.

707
00:31:52,820 --> 00:31:54,140
What about Sun?

708
00:31:55,660 --> 00:31:56,500
He...

