722
00:32:17,740 --> 00:32:18,680
How do you filter them?

723
00:32:19,180 --> 00:32:20,020
Let me ask you.

724
00:32:20,460 --> 00:32:22,460
Does every action have logic?

725
00:32:23,130 --> 00:32:24,020
So I think

726
00:32:24,330 --> 00:32:25,940
Sun Changhai will eat at Crispy Chicken.

727
00:32:25,950 --> 00:32:26,790
Not chain stores.

728
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:27,690
Do you know why?

729
00:32:29,260 --> 00:32:30,100
To save money.

730
00:32:31,420 --> 00:32:32,620
He doesn't lack money.

731
00:32:33,340 --> 00:32:34,180
Then why?

732
00:32:34,820 --> 00:32:36,540
Because this is a special time.

733
00:32:37,020 --> 00:32:38,220
His priority must be safety.

734
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:39,780
Crispy Chicken

735
00:32:40,090 --> 00:32:41,790
