737
00:32:43,330 --> 00:32:45,260
It's the safest place for him.

738
00:32:47,780 --> 00:32:49,060
What you said makes sense,

739
00:32:49,340 --> 00:32:50,540
but there are too many shops

740
00:32:50,540 --> 00:32:51,480
