741
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:52,460
How do you filter them?

742
00:32:52,460 --> 00:32:54,640
So we have to do field research,

743
00:32:54,660 --> 00:32:56,420
find the most probable place,

744
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:57,760
